  <para style="q1">And sin will<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Gr. </char><char style="fqa" closed="false">rub. </char></note> thrust itself in between buying and selling.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" />Unless <char style="add">a man </char> hold on diligently in the fear of the Lord,</para>
