  <para style="b" />
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" />Curse the whisperer and double-tongued:</para>
  <para style="q1">For he has destroyed many that were at peace.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" />A third person’s tongue has shaken many,</para>
